entries.femaleVariant: So I'm lettin' loose on this Animal. Bam, bam, bam... an' then I hear click, click, click…
Get me? Full mag of nines in this porker, an' he's still comin' at me with arms thick as thighs.
Tellin' you, if Jane hadn't dropped him, meathead woulda turned me to mulch.
Choom, nine mil's not the caliber these days. 'Gainst assholes sportin' subcutaneous weaves?
Where there's a will, though… Got your Burya RT-46, for instance.
Soviet tank, more like. Slug from that son-of-a-bitch'd drop anybody.
Might dislocate your shoulder in the process, but dude opposite's pulp.
